metadata.name: Air Hog 008
metadata.description:
This Hog is a pure hypebeast but he’s also one of the most influential pilots in the Flight Program. Will his impact be a good one? We’ll see… "Stay Muddy, Get Fly!"

Part of the Freeverse Collection by Freehand Profit which mainly finds it home over on Tezos. This Air Hog is 1 of 3, air dropped to holders of the corresponding Rare Shoe 2.0 x Freehand Profit collabs on Air Hog Reveal Day.
